QuestData.Title: Saw Dusted
QuestData.Description:
If we want to keep them from expanding into Stormsong, we need to cripple their lumber production!
They've only got so many lumberjacks running around. If we can cut some of them down, they'll be forced to reconsider their plans.
QuestData.QuestCompletionLog: Meet Felecia Gladstone near the Prototype Shredder.
QuestData.RewardText: Good work. That'll definitely put a damper on things.
